{"id":260476,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/10/维权网-被软禁的福州维权人士范燕琼呼唤自由（/","date":"2012-11-01T05:16:21Z","modified":"2012-11-01T05:16:21Z","title":"维权网 | 被软禁的福州维权人士范燕琼呼唤自由（组图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员王冬见报道）福州维权人士范燕琼自今年公开上街要求平反六四以来，一直受到地方当局的严密监控，其房前屋后不仅加装了摄像头，更有便衣</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>小时看守，令范燕琼无法过自由的生活，给其身心造成了很大的伤害，为此范燕琼向外界发出了“还我自由”的呼喊。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>附：</span><span>范燕琼声声呼唤自由！<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>自<span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span>日 以来，整整半年的时间，我一直处于被“严密监控”状态。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>然而，如此“严密监控”，在最近这几天又“更上一层楼”：我的房前屋后，不仅加装了各种监视器，也增加了不少便衣，几乎呼吸不到一丝一毫自由的空气，完全是一副杀气腾腾的人间乱象！<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>每天的我，望着这一切，承受着这一切，会不时地产生出“黑云压城城欲摧”的崩溃感。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>对此，我不得不要问一句：需要用如此强大的人力物力来对付我这样一个小女子吗？<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>为此，我不得不声声呼唤：还我自由！还我自由！！还我自由！！！<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-h5mM6bGHVUA/UJHkny81MHI/AAAAAAAAShI/jmL-QPPwMU8/s1600/%E6%A5%BC%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84%E4%BE%BF%E8%A1%A3%E4%BB%AC1.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-h5mM6bGHVUA/UJHkny81MHI/AAAAAAAAShI/jmL-QPPwMU8/s320/%E6%A5%BC%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84%E4%BE%BF%E8%A1%A3%E4%BB%AC1.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-yYjH1HMyfGM/UJHkp4Z-PYI/AAAAAAAAShQ/L_VUquduDoU/s1600/%E6%A5%BC%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84%E4%BE%BF%E8%A1%A3%E4%BB%AC2.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"211\" src=\"http